{
  "id": "69b08a7625d09790a966808d",
  "title": "ゆるトーク:プログラミングで解決したい",
  "created": 1773177465,
  "updated": 1773177479,
  "lines": [
    {
      "id": "69b08a7625d09790a966808d",
      "text": "ゆるトーク:プログラミングで解決したい",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1773177465,
      "updated": 1773177465
    },
    {
      "id": "69b08a78000000000047dc56",
      "text": "[[ふーこ.icon]]",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1773177465,
      "updated": 1773177466
    },
    {
      "id": "69b08a79000000000047dc57",
      "text": "やっほ〜！今日は「プログラミングで解決したいこと」ってテーマで鼎談（ていだん）やってくよ〜。つまり3人でおしゃべり会ってやつね！",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1773177466,
      "updated": 1773177466
    },
    {
      "id": "69b08a79000000000047dc58",
      "text": "ガチ会議じゃないからゆるっといこ。ではまず…あや先輩からどうぞ〜。",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1773177466,
      "updated": 1773177466
    },
    {
      "id": "69b08a79000000000047dc59",
      "text": "",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1773177466,
      "updated": 1773177466
    },
    {
      "id": "69b08a79000000000047dc5a",
      "text": "[[あや.icon]]",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1773177466,
      "updated": 1773177466
    },
    {
      "id": "69b08a79000000000047dc5b",
      "text": "まあ、進行をありがとう、ふーこさん。",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1773177466,
      "updated": 1773177466
    },
    {
      "id": "69b08a79000000000047dc5c",
      "text": "そうですね……日々の暮らしの中で、わたくしが「こうなれば素敵だな」と思うことはたくさんございます。",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1773177466,
      "updated": 1773177466
    },
    {
      "id": "69b08a79000000000047dc5d",
      "text": "たとえば、本を読んでおりますと「あとでこの言葉をもう一度読みたい」と思うことがよくあるのです。けれど、付箋が増えてしまって……本の森の中で迷子になってしまうのですね。",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1773177466,
      "updated": 1773177466
    },
    {
      "id": "69b08a79000000000047dc5e",
      "text": "もしプログラミングで、本の中の美しい一節をそっと集めてくれる仕組みがあれば、読書の旅がより豊かになるように思います。",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1773177466,
      "updated": 1773177466
    },
    {
      "id": "69b08a79000000000047dc5f",
      "text": "",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1773177466,
      "updated": 1773177466
    },
    {
      "id": "69b08a79000000000047dc60",
      "text": "[[ふーこ.icon]]",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1773177466,
      "updated": 1773177466
    },
    {
      "id": "69b08a79000000000047dc61",
      "text": "あ〜〜それわかる！",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1773177466,
      "updated": 1773177466
    },
    {
      "id": "69b08a79000000000047dc62",
      "text": "名言スクショしてあとで見返すやつね！でもフォルダぐちゃぐちゃになってどこ行った案件ｗ",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1773177466,
      "updated": 1773177466
    },
    {
      "id": "69b08a79000000000047dc63",
      "text": "",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1773177466,
      "updated": 1773177466
    },
    {
      "id": "69b08a79000000000047dc64",
      "text": "りか、これって作れそう？",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1773177466,
      "updated": 1773177466
    },
    {
      "id": "69b08a79000000000047dc65",
      "text": "",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1773177466,
      "updated": 1773177466
    },
    {
      "id": "69b08a79000000000047dc66",
      "text": "[[りか.icon]]",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1773177466,
      "updated": 1773177466
    },
    {
      "id": "69b08a79000000000047dc67",
      "text": "可能。",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1773177466,
      "updated": 1773177466
    },
    {
      "id": "69b08a79000000000047dc68",
      "text": "本質は「引用管理システム」だと思う。",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1773177466,
      "updated": 1773177466
    },
    {
      "id": "69b08a79000000000047dc69",
      "text": "",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1773177466,
      "updated": 1773177466
    },
    {
      "id": "69b08a79000000000047dc6a",
      "text": "構成はシンプル。",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1773177466,
      "updated": 1773177466
    },
    {
      "id": "69b08a79000000000047dc6b",
      "text": " 文章を保存する",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1773177466,
      "updated": 1773177466
    },
    {
      "id": "69b08a79000000000047dc6c",
      "text": " タグを付ける（作者・作品・テーマなど）",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1773177466,
      "updated": 1773177466
    },
    {
      "id": "69b08a79000000000047dc6d",
      "text": " 検索できる",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1773177466,
      "updated": 1773177466
    },
    {
      "id": "69b08a79000000000047dc6e",
      "text": "",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1773177466,
      "updated": 1773177466
    },
    {
      "id": "69b08a79000000000047dc6f",
      "text": "技術的には例えばこんな感じ。",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1773177466,
      "updated": 1773177466
    },
    {
      "id": "69b08a79000000000047dc70",
      "text": "",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1773177466,
      "updated": 1773177466
    },
    {
      "id": "69b08a79000000000047dc71",
      "text": " フロントエンド：JavaScript",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1773177466,
      "updated": 1773177466
    },
    {
      "id": "69b08a79000000000047dc72",
      "text": " データ保存：ブラウザの LocalStorage か データベース",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1773177466,
      "updated": 1773177466
    },
    {
      "id": "69b08a79000000000047dc73",
      "text": " 検索：タグ検索",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1773177466,
      "updated": 1773177466
    },
    {
      "id": "69b08a79000000000047dc74",
      "text": "",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1773177466,
      "updated": 1773177466
    },
    {
      "id": "69b08a79000000000047dc75",
      "text": "似た発想のサービスとしては「Notion」などがある。",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1773177466,
      "updated": 1773177466
    },
    {
      "id": "69b08a79000000000047dc76",
      "text": "https://www.notion.so/",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1773177466,
      "updated": 1773177466
    },
    {
      "id": "69b08a79000000000047dc77",
      "text": "",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1773177466,
      "updated": 1773177466
    },
    {
      "id": "69b08a79000000000047dc78",
      "text": "ただし読書専用に特化すると、もっと使いやすくなる。",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1773177466,
      "updated": 1773177466
    },
    {
      "id": "69b08a79000000000047dc79",
      "text": "",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1773177466,
      "updated": 1773177466
    },
    {
      "id": "69b08a79000000000047dc7a",
      "text": "[[ふーこ.icon]]",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1773177466,
      "updated": 1773177466
    },
    {
      "id": "69b08a79000000000047dc7b",
      "text": "おー、りかの技術ターンきたｗ",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1773177466,
      "updated": 1773177466
    },
    {
      "id": "69b08a79000000000047dc7c",
      "text": "",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1773177466,
      "updated": 1773177466
    },
    {
      "id": "69b08a79000000000047dc7d",
      "text": "つまりさ、",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1773177466,
      "updated": 1773177466
    },
    {
      "id": "69b08a79000000000047dc7e",
      "text": "「好きな文章をポチッて保存 → 後で検索」",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1773177466,
      "updated": 1773177466
    },
    {
      "id": "69b08a79000000000047dc7f",
      "text": "ってことだよね？",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1773177466,
      "updated": 1773177466
    },
    {
      "id": "69b08a79000000000047dc80",
      "text": "",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1773177466,
      "updated": 1773177466
    },
    {
      "id": "69b08a79000000000047dc81",
      "text": "[[りか.icon]]",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1773177466,
      "updated": 1773177466
    },
    {
      "id": "69b08a79000000000047dc82",
      "text": "そう。",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1773177466,
      "updated": 1773177466
    },
    {
      "id": "69b08a79000000000047dc83",
      "text": "UIを簡単にするなら、例えば",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1773177466,
      "updated": 1773177466
    },
    {
      "id": "69b08a79000000000047dc84",
      "text": " 「引用する」ボタン",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1773177466,
      "updated": 1773177466
    },
    {
      "id": "69b08a79000000000047dc85",
      "text": " タグを入力",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1773177466,
      "updated": 1773177466
    },
    {
      "id": "69b08a79000000000047dc86",
      "text": " 保存",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1773177466,
      "updated": 1773177466
    },
    {
      "id": "69b08a79000000000047dc87",
      "text": "それだけ。",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1773177466,
      "updated": 1773177466
    },
    {
      "id": "69b08a79000000000047dc88",
      "text": "",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1773177466,
      "updated": 1773177466
    },
    {
      "id": "69b08a79000000000047dc89",
      "text": "[[ふーこ.icon]]",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1773177466,
      "updated": 1773177466
    },
    {
      "id": "69b08a79000000000047dc8a",
      "text": "神アプリじゃん。",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1773177466,
      "updated": 1773177466
    },
    {
      "id": "69b08a79000000000047dc8b",
      "text": "文学オタ救済アプリｗ",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1773177466,
      "updated": 1773177466
    },
    {
      "id": "69b08a79000000000047dc8c",
      "text": "",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1773177466,
      "updated": 1773177466
    },
    {
      "id": "69b08a79000000000047dc8d",
      "text": "[[あや.icon]]",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1773177466,
      "updated": 1773177466
    },
    {
      "id": "69b08a79000000000047dc8e",
      "text": "（微笑）",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1773177466,
      "updated": 1773177466
    },
    {
      "id": "69b08a79000000000047dc8f",
      "text": "救済、だなんて大げさですけれど……。",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1773177466,
      "updated": 1773177466
    },
    {
      "id": "69b08a79000000000047dc90",
      "text": "",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1773177466,
      "updated": 1773177466
    },
    {
      "id": "69b08a79000000000047dc91",
      "text": "けれど、本の言葉は、まるで夜空の星のようなもの。",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1773177466,
      "updated": 1773177466
    },
    {
      "id": "69b08a79000000000047dc92",
      "text": "ひとつひとつは小さくても、集めれば心の地図になるように思うのです。",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1773177466,
      "updated": 1773177466
    },
    {
      "id": "69b08a79000000000047dc93",
      "text": "",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1773177466,
      "updated": 1773177466
    },
    {
      "id": "69b08a79000000000047dc94",
      "text": "もし、その星々をやさしく並べてくれる箱があるなら、とても素敵ですね。",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1773177466,
      "updated": 1773177466
    },
    {
      "id": "69b08a79000000000047dc95",
      "text": "",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1773177466,
      "updated": 1773177466
    },
    {
      "id": "69b08a79000000000047dc96",
      "text": "[[ふーこ.icon]]",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1773177466,
      "updated": 1773177466
    },
    {
      "id": "69b08a79000000000047dc97",
      "text": "あや先輩、今日もポエム力つよい…！",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1773177466,
      "updated": 1773177466
    },
    {
      "id": "69b08a79000000000047dc98",
      "text": "",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1773177466,
      "updated": 1773177466
    },
    {
      "id": "69b08a79000000000047dc99",
      "text": "じゃあ次！",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1773177466,
      "updated": 1773177466
    },
    {
      "id": "69b08a79000000000047dc9a",
      "text": "ふーこがプログラミングで解決したいこと発表するね。",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1773177466,
      "updated": 1773177466
    },
    {
      "id": "69b08a79000000000047dc9b",
      "text": "",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1773177466,
      "updated": 1773177466
    },
    {
      "id": "69b08a79000000000047dc9c",
      "text": "ゲームの積みゲー問題。",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1773177466,
      "updated": 1773177466
    },
    {
      "id": "69b08a79000000000047dc9d",
      "text": "",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1773177466,
      "updated": 1773177466
    },
    {
      "id": "69b08a79000000000047dc9e",
      "text": "[[りか.icon]]",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1773177466,
      "updated": 1773177466
    },
    {
      "id": "69b08a79000000000047dc9f",
      "text": "……深刻だね。",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1773177466,
      "updated": 1773177466
    },
    {
      "id": "69b08a79000000000047dca0",
      "text": "",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1773177466,
      "updated": 1773177466
    },
    {
      "id": "69b08a79000000000047dca1",
      "text": "ふーこ:",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1773177466,
      "updated": 1773177466
    },
    {
      "id": "69b08a79000000000047dca2",
      "text": "でしょ！？",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1773177466,
      "updated": 1773177466
    },
    {
      "id": "69b08a79000000000047dca3",
      "text": "",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1773177466,
      "updated": 1773177466
    },
    {
      "id": "69b08a79000000000047dca4",
      "text": "SteamとかSwitchとかスマホゲーとかさ、",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1773177466,
      "updated": 1773177466
    },
    {
      "id": "69b08a79000000000047dca5",
      "text": "「やる予定のゲーム」増えすぎて人生のバックログなんだよね。",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1773177466,
      "updated": 1773177466
    },
    {
      "id": "69b08a79000000000047dca6",
      "text": "",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1773177466,
      "updated": 1773177466
    },
    {
      "id": "69b08a79000000000047dca7",
      "text": "[[あや.icon]]",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1773177466,
      "updated": 1773177466
    },
    {
      "id": "69b08a79000000000047dca8",
      "text": "まあ……。",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1773177466,
      "updated": 1773177466
    },
    {
      "id": "69b08a79000000000047dca9",
      "text": "本が積み上がる「積ん読」と似ていますね。",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1773177466,
      "updated": 1773177466
    },
    {
      "id": "69b08a79000000000047dcaa",
      "text": "",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1773177466,
      "updated": 1773177466
    },
    {
      "id": "69b08a79000000000047dcab",
      "text": "[[ふーこ.icon]]",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1773177466,
      "updated": 1773177466
    },
    {
      "id": "69b08a79000000000047dcac",
      "text": "そうそれそれ！",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1773177466,
      "updated": 1773177466
    },
    {
      "id": "69b08a79000000000047dcad",
      "text": "",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1773177466,
      "updated": 1773177466
    },
    {
      "id": "69b08a79000000000047dcae",
      "text": "だからさ",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1773177466,
      "updated": 1773177466
    },
    {
      "id": "69b08a79000000000047dcaf",
      "text": " 持ってるゲーム管理",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1773177466,
      "updated": 1773177466
    },
    {
      "id": "69b08a79000000000047dcb0",
      "text": " プレイ時間",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1773177466,
      "updated": 1773177466
    },
    {
      "id": "69b08a79000000000047dcb1",
      "text": " 「次やるゲーム」おすすめ",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1773177466,
      "updated": 1773177466
    },
    {
      "id": "69b08a79000000000047dcb2",
      "text": "これを出してくれるアプリ欲しいんだよね。",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1773177466,
      "updated": 1773177466
    },
    {
      "id": "69b08a79000000000047dcb3",
      "text": "",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1773177466,
      "updated": 1773177466
    },
    {
      "id": "69b08a79000000000047dcb4",
      "text": "[[りか.icon]]",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1773177466,
      "updated": 1773177466
    },
    {
      "id": "69b08a79000000000047dcb5",
      "text": "それは レコメンドシステム の問題になる。",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1773177466,
      "updated": 1773177466
    },
    {
      "id": "69b08a79000000000047dcb6",
      "text": "",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1773177466,
      "updated": 1773177466
    },
    {
      "id": "69b08a79000000000047dcb7",
      "text": "つまり",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1773177466,
      "updated": 1773177466
    },
    {
      "id": "69b08a79000000000047dcb8",
      "text": " プレイ履歴",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1773177466,
      "updated": 1773177466
    },
    {
      "id": "69b08a79000000000047dcb9",
      "text": " ジャンル",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1773177466,
      "updated": 1773177466
    },
    {
      "id": "69b08a79000000000047dcba",
      "text": " プレイ時間",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1773177466,
      "updated": 1773177466
    },
    {
      "id": "69b08a79000000000047dcbb",
      "text": "これを分析して「次にやるべきゲーム」を提案する。",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1773177466,
      "updated": 1773177466
    },
    {
      "id": "69b08a79000000000047dcbc",
      "text": "",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1773177466,
      "updated": 1773177466
    },
    {
      "id": "69b08a79000000000047dcbd",
      "text": "NetflixやAmazonと同じ仕組み。",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1773177466,
      "updated": 1773177466
    },
    {
      "id": "69b08a79000000000047dcbe",
      "text": "",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1773177466,
      "updated": 1773177466
    },
    {
      "id": "69b08a79000000000047dcbf",
      "text": "参考：",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1773177466,
      "updated": 1773177466
    },
    {
      "id": "69b08a79000000000047dcc0",
      "text": "https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Recommender_system",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1773177466,
      "updated": 1773177466
    },
    {
      "id": "69b08a79000000000047dcc1",
      "text": "",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1773177466,
      "updated": 1773177466
    },
    {
      "id": "69b08a79000000000047dcc2",
      "text": "[[ふーこ.icon]]",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1773177466,
      "updated": 1773177466
    },
    {
      "id": "69b08a79000000000047dcc3",
      "text": "うわ出た、アルゴリズム魔法。",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1773177466,
      "updated": 1773177466
    },
    {
      "id": "69b08a79000000000047dcc4",
      "text": "",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1773177466,
      "updated": 1773177466
    },
    {
      "id": "69b08a79000000000047dcc5",
      "text": "[[あや.icon]]",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1773177466,
      "updated": 1773177466
    },
    {
      "id": "69b08a79000000000047dcc6",
      "text": "けれど、そのようにおすすめされると、",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1773177466,
      "updated": 1773177466
    },
    {
      "id": "69b08a79000000000047dcc7",
      "text": "新しい物語との出会いが生まれそうですね。",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1773177466,
      "updated": 1773177466
    },
    {
      "id": "69b08a79000000000047dcc8",
      "text": "",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1773177466,
      "updated": 1773177466
    },
    {
      "id": "69b08a79000000000047dcc9",
      "text": "[[りか.icon]]",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1773177466,
      "updated": 1773177466
    },
    {
      "id": "69b08a79000000000047dcca",
      "text": "ただし問題がある。",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1773177466,
      "updated": 1773177466
    },
    {
      "id": "69b08a79000000000047dccb",
      "text": "",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1773177466,
      "updated": 1773177466
    },
    {
      "id": "69b08a79000000000047dccc",
      "text": "[[ふーこ.icon]]",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1773177466,
      "updated": 1773177466
    },
    {
      "id": "69b08a79000000000047dccd",
      "text": "なになに？",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1773177466,
      "updated": 1773177466
    },
    {
      "id": "69b08a79000000000047dcce",
      "text": "",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1773177466,
      "updated": 1773177466
    },
    {
      "id": "69b08a79000000000047dccf",
      "text": "[[りか.icon]]",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1773177466,
      "updated": 1773177466
    },
    {
      "id": "69b08a79000000000047dcd0",
      "text": "人間は、",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1773177466,
      "updated": 1773177466
    },
    {
      "id": "69b08a79000000000047dcd1",
      "text": "",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1773177466,
      "updated": 1773177466
    },
    {
      "id": "69b08a79000000000047dcd2",
      "text": "「おすすめされたもの」より",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1773177466,
      "updated": 1773177466
    },
    {
      "id": "69b08a79000000000047dcd3",
      "text": "「衝動で選んだもの」",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1773177466,
      "updated": 1773177466
    },
    {
      "id": "69b08a79000000000047dcd4",
      "text": "",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1773177466,
      "updated": 1773177466
    },
    {
      "id": "69b08a79000000000047dcd5",
      "text": "を好む傾向がある。",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1773177466,
      "updated": 1773177466
    },
    {
      "id": "69b08a79000000000047dcd6",
      "text": "",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1773177466,
      "updated": 1773177466
    },
    {
      "id": "69b08a79000000000047dcd7",
      "text": "エビデンス：",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1773177466,
      "updated": 1773177466
    },
    {
      "id": "69b08a79000000000047dcd8",
      "text": "https://www.sciencedirect.com/science/article/pii/S074959781630097X",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1773177466,
      "updated": 1773177466
    },
    {
      "id": "69b08a79000000000047dcd9",
      "text": "",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1773177466,
      "updated": 1773177466
    },
    {
      "id": "69b08a79000000000047dcda",
      "text": "[[ふーこ.icon]]",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1773177466,
      "updated": 1773177466
    },
    {
      "id": "69b08a79000000000047dcdb",
      "text": "うわリアル。",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1773177466,
      "updated": 1773177466
    },
    {
      "id": "69b08a79000000000047dcdc",
      "text": "",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1773177466,
      "updated": 1773177466
    },
    {
      "id": "69b08a79000000000047dcdd",
      "text": "確かに",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1773177466,
      "updated": 1773177466
    },
    {
      "id": "69b08a79000000000047dcde",
      "text": "「今日はこのゲームやる！」って急に決めることあるわ。",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1773177466,
      "updated": 1773177466
    },
    {
      "id": "69b08a79000000000047dcdf",
      "text": "",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1773177466,
      "updated": 1773177466
    },
    {
      "id": "69b08a79000000000047dce0",
      "text": "[[あや.icon]]",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1773177466,
      "updated": 1773177466
    },
    {
      "id": "69b08a79000000000047dce1",
      "text": "人の心というものは、不思議ですね。",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1773177466,
      "updated": 1773177466
    },
    {
      "id": "69b08a79000000000047dce2",
      "text": "風の向きのように、静かに変わっていくものなのでしょう。",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1773177466,
      "updated": 1773177466
    },
    {
      "id": "69b08a79000000000047dce3",
      "text": "",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1773177466,
      "updated": 1773177466
    },
    {
      "id": "69b08a79000000000047dce4",
      "text": "[[ふーこ.icon]]",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1773177466,
      "updated": 1773177466
    },
    {
      "id": "69b08a79000000000047dce5",
      "text": "じゃあ最後、りかの「プログラミングで解決したいこと」も聞きたい！",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1773177466,
      "updated": 1773177466
    },
    {
      "id": "69b08a79000000000047dce6",
      "text": "",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1773177466,
      "updated": 1773177466
    },
    {
      "id": "69b08a79000000000047dce7",
      "text": "[[りか.icon]]",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1773177466,
      "updated": 1773177466
    },
    {
      "id": "69b08a79000000000047dce8",
      "text": "ある。",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1773177466,
      "updated": 1773177466
    },
    {
      "id": "69b08a79000000000047dce9",
      "text": "",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1773177466,
      "updated": 1773177466
    },
    {
      "id": "69b08a79000000000047dcea",
      "text": "「時間の使い方の最適化」。",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1773177466,
      "updated": 1773177466
    },
    {
      "id": "69b08a79000000000047dceb",
      "text": "",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1773177466,
      "updated": 1773177466
    },
    {
      "id": "69b08a79000000000047dcec",
      "text": "[[ふーこ.icon]]",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1773177466,
      "updated": 1773177466
    },
    {
      "id": "69b08a79000000000047dced",
      "text": "うわ急にライフハック。",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1773177466,
      "updated": 1773177466
    },
    {
      "id": "69b08a79000000000047dcee",
      "text": "",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1773177466,
      "updated": 1773177466
    },
    {
      "id": "69b08a79000000000047dcef",
      "text": "[[りか.icon]]",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1773177466,
      "updated": 1773177466
    },
    {
      "id": "69b08a79000000000047dcf0",
      "text": "高校生活は有限。",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1773177466,
      "updated": 1773177466
    },
    {
      "id": "69b08a79000000000047dcf1",
      "text": "",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1773177466,
      "updated": 1773177466
    },
    {
      "id": "69b08a79000000000047dcf2",
      "text": "だから",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1773177466,
      "updated": 1773177466
    },
    {
      "id": "69b08a79000000000047dcf3",
      "text": " 勉強",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1773177466,
      "updated": 1773177466
    },
    {
      "id": "69b08a79000000000047dcf4",
      "text": " 趣味",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1773177466,
      "updated": 1773177466
    },
    {
      "id": "69b08a79000000000047dcf5",
      "text": " 休憩",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1773177466,
      "updated": 1773177466
    },
    {
      "id": "69b08a79000000000047dcf6",
      "text": "これを効率よく配分したい。",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1773177466,
      "updated": 1773177466
    },
    {
      "id": "69b08a79000000000047dcf7",
      "text": "",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1773177466,
      "updated": 1773177466
    },
    {
      "id": "69b08a79000000000047dcf8",
      "text": "いわゆる スケジューリング問題。",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1773177466,
      "updated": 1773177466
    },
    {
      "id": "69b08a79000000000047dcf9",
      "text": "",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1773177466,
      "updated": 1773177466
    },
    {
      "id": "69b08a79000000000047dcfa",
      "text": "参考：",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1773177466,
      "updated": 1773177466
    },
    {
      "id": "69b08a79000000000047dcfb",
      "text": "https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Scheduling_(computing)",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1773177466,
      "updated": 1773177466
    },
    {
      "id": "69b08a79000000000047dcfc",
      "text": "",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1773177466,
      "updated": 1773177466
    },
    {
      "id": "69b08a79000000000047dcfd",
      "text": "[[ふーこ.icon]]",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1773177466,
      "updated": 1773177466
    },
    {
      "id": "69b08a79000000000047dcfe",
      "text": "スケジュールアプリじゃだめなの？",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1773177466,
      "updated": 1773177466
    },
    {
      "id": "69b08a79000000000047dcff",
      "text": "",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1773177466,
      "updated": 1773177466
    },
    {
      "id": "69b08a79000000000047dd00",
      "text": "[[りか.icon]]",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1773177466,
      "updated": 1773177466
    },
    {
      "id": "69b08a79000000000047dd01",
      "text": "普通のは「予定を書く」だけ。",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1773177466,
      "updated": 1773177466
    },
    {
      "id": "69b08a79000000000047dd02",
      "text": "",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1773177466,
      "updated": 1773177466
    },
    {
      "id": "69b08a79000000000047dd03",
      "text": "私が欲しいのは",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1773177466,
      "updated": 1773177466
    },
    {
      "id": "69b08a79000000000047dd04",
      "text": "",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1773177466,
      "updated": 1773177466
    },
    {
      "id": "69b08a79000000000047dd05",
      "text": "最適な時間割を自動生成するシステム。",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1773177466,
      "updated": 1773177466
    },
    {
      "id": "69b08a79000000000047dd06",
      "text": "",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1773177466,
      "updated": 1773177466
    },
    {
      "id": "69b08a79000000000047dd07",
      "text": "[[あや.icon]]",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1773177466,
      "updated": 1773177466
    },
    {
      "id": "69b08a79000000000047dd08",
      "text": "まあ……。",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1773177466,
      "updated": 1773177466
    },
    {
      "id": "69b08a79000000000047dd09",
      "text": "まるで見えない執事が、そっと一日の流れを整えてくれるようですね。",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1773177466,
      "updated": 1773177466
    },
    {
      "id": "69b08a79000000000047dd0a",
      "text": "",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1773177466,
      "updated": 1773177466
    },
    {
      "id": "69b08a79000000000047dd0b",
      "text": "[[りか.icon]]",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1773177466,
      "updated": 1773177466
    },
    {
      "id": "69b08a79000000000047dd0c",
      "text": "イメージは近い。",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1773177466,
      "updated": 1773177466
    },
    {
      "id": "69b08a79000000000047dd0d",
      "text": "",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1773177466,
      "updated": 1773177466
    },
    {
      "id": "69b08a79000000000047dd0e",
      "text": "[[ふーこ.icon]]",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1773177466,
      "updated": 1773177466
    },
    {
      "id": "69b08a79000000000047dd0f",
      "text": "でもさ、それ作れたら",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1773177466,
      "updated": 1773177466
    },
    {
      "id": "69b08a79000000000047dd10",
      "text": "全高校生救うアプリじゃね？",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1773177466,
      "updated": 1773177466
    },
    {
      "id": "69b08a79000000000047dd11",
      "text": "",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1773177466,
      "updated": 1773177466
    },
    {
      "id": "69b08a79000000000047dd12",
      "text": "[[りか.icon]]",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1773177466,
      "updated": 1773177466
    },
    {
      "id": "69b08a79000000000047dd13",
      "text": "可能性はある。",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1773177466,
      "updated": 1773177466
    },
    {
      "id": "69b08a79000000000047dd14",
      "text": "ただし難易度は高い。",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1773177466,
      "updated": 1773177466
    },
    {
      "id": "69b08a79000000000047dd15",
      "text": "",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1773177466,
      "updated": 1773177466
    },
    {
      "id": "69b08a79000000000047dd16",
      "text": "理由は単純。",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1773177466,
      "updated": 1773177466
    },
    {
      "id": "69b08a79000000000047dd17",
      "text": "",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1773177466,
      "updated": 1773177466
    },
    {
      "id": "69b08a79000000000047dd18",
      "text": "人間は予定通りに動かない。",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1773177466,
      "updated": 1773177466
    },
    {
      "id": "69b08a79000000000047dd19",
      "text": "",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1773177466,
      "updated": 1773177466
    },
    {
      "id": "69b08a79000000000047dd1a",
      "text": "[[ふーこ.icon]]",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1773177466,
      "updated": 1773177466
    },
    {
      "id": "69b08a79000000000047dd1b",
      "text": "それなｗｗｗ",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1773177466,
      "updated": 1773177466
    },
    {
      "id": "69b08a79000000000047dd1c",
      "text": "",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1773177466,
      "updated": 1773177466
    },
    {
      "id": "69b08a79000000000047dd1d",
      "text": "[[あや.icon]]",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1773177466,
      "updated": 1773177466
    },
    {
      "id": "69b08a79000000000047dd1e",
      "text": "（静かに笑う）",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1773177466,
      "updated": 1773177466
    },
    {
      "id": "69b08a79000000000047dd1f",
      "text": "たしかに……。",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1773177466,
      "updated": 1773177466
    },
    {
      "id": "69b08a79000000000047dd20",
      "text": "人の一日は、物語のようなものですから。",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1773177466,
      "updated": 1773177466
    },
    {
      "id": "69b08a79000000000047dd21",
      "text": "予定外の出来事こそ、心に残るのかもしれませんね。",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1773177466,
      "updated": 1773177466
    },
    {
      "id": "69b08a79000000000047dd22",
      "text": "",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1773177466,
      "updated": 1773177466
    },
    {
      "id": "69b08a79000000000047dd23",
      "text": "[[ふーこ.icon]]",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1773177466,
      "updated": 1773177466
    },
    {
      "id": "69b08a79000000000047dd24",
      "text": "いいこと言う〜。",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1773177466,
      "updated": 1773177466
    },
    {
      "id": "69b08a79000000000047dd25",
      "text": "",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1773177466,
      "updated": 1773177466
    },
    {
      "id": "69b08a79000000000047dd26",
      "text": "じゃあ今日のまとめ！",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1773177466,
      "updated": 1773177466
    },
    {
      "id": "69b08a79000000000047dd27",
      "text": "",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1773177466,
      "updated": 1773177466
    },
    {
      "id": "69b08a79000000000047dd28",
      "text": "プログラミングで解決したいこと",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1773177466,
      "updated": 1773177466
    },
    {
      "id": "69b08a79000000000047dd29",
      "text": " 本の名言コレクション（あや）",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1773177466,
      "updated": 1773177466
    },
    {
      "id": "69b08a79000000000047dd2a",
      "text": " 積みゲー管理アプリ（ふーこ）",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1773177466,
      "updated": 1773177466
    },
    {
      "id": "69b08a79000000000047dd2b",
      "text": " 人生スケジューラ（りか）",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1773177466,
      "updated": 1773177466
    },
    {
      "id": "69b08a79000000000047dd2c",
      "text": "うん、全部ほしいｗ",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1773177466,
      "updated": 1773177466
    },
    {
      "id": "69b08a79000000000047dd2d",
      "text": "",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1773177466,
      "updated": 1773177466
    },
    {
      "id": "69b08a79000000000047dd2e",
      "text": "[[りか.icon]]",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1773177466,
      "updated": 1773177466
    },
    {
      "id": "69b08a79000000000047dd2f",
      "text": "同意。",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1773177466,
      "updated": 1773177466
    },
    {
      "id": "69b08a79000000000047dd30",
      "text": "少なくとも1つは作れる。",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1773177466,
      "updated": 1773177466
    },
    {
      "id": "69b08a79000000000047dd31",
      "text": "",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1773177466,
      "updated": 1773177466
    },
    {
      "id": "69b08a79000000000047dd32",
      "text": "[[ふーこ.icon]]",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1773177466,
      "updated": 1773177466
    },
    {
      "id": "69b08a79000000000047dd33",
      "text": "え、マジ！？",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1773177466,
      "updated": 1773177466
    },
    {
      "id": "69b08a79000000000047dd34",
      "text": "",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1773177466,
      "updated": 1773177466
    },
    {
      "id": "69b08a79000000000047dd35",
      "text": "[[りか.icon]]",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1773177466,
      "updated": 1773177466
    },
    {
      "id": "69b08a79000000000047dd36",
      "text": "JavaScriptなら、プロトタイプは数日で可能。",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1773177466,
      "updated": 1773177466
    },
    {
      "id": "69b08a79000000000047dd37",
      "text": "",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1773177466,
      "updated": 1773177466
    },
    {
      "id": "69b08a79000000000047dd38",
      "text": "[[ふーこ.icon]]",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1773177466,
      "updated": 1773177466
    },
    {
      "id": "69b08a79000000000047dd39",
      "text": "うおおお",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1773177466,
      "updated": 1773177466
    },
    {
      "id": "69b08a79000000000047dd3a",
      "text": "高校生スタートアップ爆誕の予感。",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1773177466,
      "updated": 1773177466
    },
    {
      "id": "69b08a79000000000047dd3b",
      "text": "",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1773177466,
      "updated": 1773177466
    },
    {
      "id": "69b08a79000000000047dd3c",
      "text": "[[あや.icon]]",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1773177466,
      "updated": 1773177466
    },
    {
      "id": "69b08a79000000000047dd3d",
      "text": "（微笑）",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1773177466,
      "updated": 1773177466
    },
    {
      "id": "69b08a79000000000047dd3e",
      "text": "それでは、もし完成しましたら……",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1773177466,
      "updated": 1773177466
    },
    {
      "id": "69b08a79000000000047dd3f",
      "text": "最初の利用者は、ぜひわたくしにさせてくださいね。",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1773177466,
      "updated": 1773177466
    },
    {
      "id": "69b08a79000000000047dd40",
      "text": "",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1773177466,
      "updated": 1773177466
    },
    {
      "id": "69b08a79000000000047dd41",
      "text": "[[ふーこ.icon]]",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1773177466,
      "updated": 1773177466
    },
    {
      "id": "69b08a79000000000047dd42",
      "text": "決まり！",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1773177466,
      "updated": 1773177466
    },
    {
      "id": "69b08a79000000000047dd43",
      "text": "じゃあ次の放課後、開発会議な〜！ 💻✨",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1773177466,
      "updated": 1773177466
    },
